xxl.core.spatial.geometries
Interface Point2D

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Geometry2D>, Geometry2D, java.io.Serializable
public interface Point2D
extends Geometry2D

A Point2D is a 0-dimensional geometry and represents a single location in coordinate space. It has a x-coordinate value and a y-coordinate value and its boundary is the empty set.

See Simple Feature Specification (pdf).
